reen></iframe></p><p></p><p> “As Geppetto&#39;s deadly puppet, you&#39;ll journey through Krat and its surroundings, uncover hidden backstories, and face epic battles that shape the past and future of <em>Lies Of P</em> ,” reads the <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2848330/Lies_of_P_Overture/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">official description</a> . “Dare to unravel the mysteries of the past, for in the heart of darkness lies the key to unlocking the secrets of a timeless tale reborn.”</p><p> “We knew that the end of <em>Lies Of P</em> was just the beginning for what our team had in store for fans,” said game director Jiwon Choi. “ <em>Lies Of P: Overture</em> allows us the opportunity to fully explore the past and present of our universe. We are grateful for our community&#39;s patience as our team took the time to tell the story we&#39;ve always wanted to share.”</p><p> “For the DLC and the sequel, we aim to do better on what we did well and improve in areas we have room to grow,” he explained last year. “这听起来很简单，但是我发现坚持基础知识并不容易。 We hope to turn your anticipation into delight.”</p><p> In other news, the long-awaited remake of <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/metal-gear-solid-3-snake-eater">Metal Gear Solid Delta: Snake Eater</a></em> finally has a release date, with developers saying their “ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/metal-gear-solid-3-delta-snake-eater-release-date-price-preorder-3837651">most important mission was not to let the fans down</a> ”.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/lies-of-p-overture-dlc-release-date-3837672">&#39;Lies Of P&#39; is getting a prequel expansion this summer</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
